# GIF API System

Using Klipy:

Endpoint:

```

[https://api.klipy.com/v2/search](https://api.klipy.com/v2/search)

```

Correct response parsing:

```

payload["results"]

item["media_formats"]["gif"]["url"]

```

Created:

```

utils/gif_api.py

```

Function:

```

fetch_gif(query)

```

It:
- sends async request
- gets GIF results
- randomly chooses a GIF
- returns URL

