# Cooldown System

Created:

```

utils/cooldowns.py

```

Implemented:

## Normal command cooldown

Examples:

```

.rizz
.rizz @someone

```

Cooldown:

```

3 seconds

```

---

## Multi-target cooldown

Example:

```

.rizz @A @B @C

```

Cooldown:

```

10 minutes

```

